cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL 

The paper proposes a method for training deep neural networks using auto-encoders and target propagation. This approach is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science, including machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and natural language processing (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on deep learning and neural networks, cs.LG and cs.NE are the most likely sub-categories.
